name: Debbie Boyde
description:
Not my best work, which is largely due to the fact that Debbie Boyde only ever did two photoshoots and all the other photos of her available are terrible quality mobile 'phone photos.

As a result, you'll often need some quite strong prompting and the backgrounds have a strong tendency to look like the locations her two photoshoots were done in.
